com.viaoa.remote.multiplexer.info

Class BindInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.viaoa.remote.multiplexer.info.BindInfo

  • public class BindInfo
extends Object
    Internal information about a remote Object. One side (Client/Server) will have the real object, and the other side will have a proxy. Any reference that is passed between the C/S will use the name, and then replaced with the real/proxy instance by the receiving side.
    Author:
    vvia
